    public class XacmlCSVEngine
extends java.lang.Object
implements ConfigurableEngine
    CSVPIPEngine implements the PIPFinder interface to find attributes loaded from a text file containing the following fields: category-id,attribute-id,datatype-id,issuer,value

        public PIPResponse getAttributes(PIPRequest pipRequest,
                        PIPFinder pipFinder)
                          throws PIPException
        Description copied from interface: PIPEngine
        Retrieves Attributes that match the given PIPRequest. The PIPResponse may contain multiple Attributes and they do not need to match the PIPRequest. In this way, a PIPEngine may compute multiple related Attributes at once.
        Specified by:
        getAttributes in interface PIPEngine
        Parameters:
